                                <li><strong>Memory Vault:</strong> Revisiting and organizing important memories</li>
                                <li><strong>Emotional Processing:</strong> Working through complex feelings</li>
                                <li><strong>Creative Exploration:</strong> Generating new perspectives and ideas</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Rituals help create a meaningful rhythm to the relationship with MeX, balancing structure with spontaneity.</p>
